				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\overrightarrow{F}$$\end{document}) in a small region (~ 0.5 a0) in the middle of the vacuum to ensure periodicity. Calculations are performed with F→\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
